ons/icon3.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/10/02 2:41:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4373.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   which weapon to keep</span><hr size=1> I am lvl 51 soon(45 now and use SBoZ + 1hb) and have pair of Fleshgrinder, Wavecrasher, 1hb(12/20), 1hp(10/1<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> , and possible get Frostbringer if really good, and plan to get Windblade soon(watching price to drop atm)<br>
<br>
I heard many post about Windblade are very good for dps, but how much more DSP from Windblade compare to FG/FG ?<br>
<br>
how often should I use Windblade and which weapon I should sell/banked away ? this is tweak and I ususlly group/duo <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=slycindyce2>Slycin Dyce2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/10/02 3:39:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4373.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: which weapon to keep</span><hr size=1> matters which you want.. DPS or Aggro...<br>
<br>
<br>
aggro, i think the WC and FG would be nice(that is like MT style aggro)<br>
<br>
Good mix of DPS/Aggro would be FG and 12/20 1hb in secondary<br>
<br>
<br>
And there is a reason the windblade is arguably the best weapon that is sellable out right now <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pertietrull>PertieTrull</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/10/02 7:43:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4373.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   re</span><hr size=1> I think he is looking for a bit more specific information with numbers. I am in a similar situation, I know everyone says windblade is best for dps, but how much better I dont really know. Having 1 combo (fg/fg or fg/fb) that I can use all the time would be nicer than having to switch out all the time. If fg/fg or fg/fb is only a bit lower dps, or a bit more agro than windblade that makes the decision easier. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thorilan>thorilan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 268<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/10/02 8:09:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4373.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: re</span><hr size=1> the weapons i would keep are 2 FG and the windblade. the wavecrasher is nice but only if you want to MT some of the low end content which there isnt much of . and if you have these others availible to you you will pass that content up real quick<br>
<br>
i would also ask about your haste atm too.<br>
<br>
personaly i use 2x FG even for DPS because it is still very high and with high dex it procs a lot . enough to put its dps very high. ( gotta love getting shammy buffs) <br>
so FG x2 gives good dps AND agro . the wind blade does great damage but if you can swing it i would get both<br>
<br>
<br>
