<br>
It goes down in damage the further u are away from 56 btw.  At lvl 54, It's stats were 48/44 and at 55 now its 49/44.  <br>
<br>
Id say that it depends on the mobs you are fighting.  Here are a few kinds of mobs . . . <br>
<br>
1) Hight defensive, ie blocks a lot<br>
2) High riposite<br>
3) High AC, midigation<br>
4) Many attacks<br>
<br>
2 Handers usually work better against High AC and high riposite mobs due to damage actually getting thru and less riposite attacks vrs duel wield.  Some mobs it seems like I cant even hit em with 2 handers (miss miss miss) and when I switch to duel wield, Im golden.<br>
<br>
Its very situational so play round with them and u'll know what to use.<br>
